'''席德·西泽'''（{{lang-en|Sid Caesar, Isaac Sidney Caesar}}，{{bd|1922年|9月8日|2014年|2月12日|catIdx=Caesar}}）纽约人，是一名美国喜剧演员。他在1950年的《{{link-en|你的演出的演出|Your Show of Shows}}》和《{{link-en|凯撒时间|Caesar's Hour}}》开始职业生涯，此前他是一名音乐家<ref>{{cite web |url=http://movies.nytimes.com/person/10145/Sid-Caesar/biography |title=Sid Caesar - Biography - Movies & TV - NYTimes.com |work=movies.nytimes.com |year=2011 [last update] |accessdate=February 22, 2011 |archive-date=2008-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081208053342/http://movies.nytimes.com/person/10145/Sid-Caesar/biography }}</ref>；职业生涯中他获得两次[[艾美奖|艾美奖]]。

席德·西泽是[[猶太人|猶太人]]，他的父母是來自俄羅斯和波蘭的猶太移民<ref>{{Cite web|title=Interview: Sid Caesar|url=https://www.thejc.com/culture/interviews/interview-sid-caesar-1.18603|accessdate=June 25, 2019|date=October 7, 2010|last=Paskin|first=Barbra|format=|publisher=The Jewish Chronicle|archive-date=2021-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210707035530/https://www.thejc.com/culture/interviews/interview-sid-caesar-1.18603}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=With a Jewish-infused style, Sid Caesar revolutionized television comedy|url=http://jewishstandard.timesofisrael.com/with-a-jewish-infused-style-sid-caesar-revolutionized-television-comedy/|accessdate=June 25, 2019|date=March 21, 2014|publisher=The Jewish Standard|archive-date=2022-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220618224923/https://jewishstandard.timesofisrael.com/with-a-jewish-infused-style-sid-caesar-revolutionized-television-comedy/}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_g1epc/is_bio/ai_2419200176 |work=St. James Encyclopedia of Pop Culture |title=Sid Caesar |first=Susan |last=Murray |year=2002 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120710182636/http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_g1epc/is_bio/ai_2419200176/ |archivedate=2012-07-10 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.filmreference.com/film/70/Sid-Caesar.html |title=Sid Caesar Biography (1922-)<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2014-02-14 |archive-date=2022-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220614083631/http://www.filmreference.com/film/70/Sid-Caesar.html }}</ref>。他有三个孩子。

2014年2月12日，他因为自然原因死于美國加利福尼亞州洛杉磯[[比佛利山|比佛利山]]，享年91歲<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sid Caesar Dead: Comedy Titan Was 91|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/sid-caesar-dead-comedy-titan-679817|accessdate=June 25, 2019|date=February 12, 2014|last=Barnes|first=Mike|publisher=The Hollywood Reporter|archive-date=2021-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415021449/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/sid-caesar-dead-comedy-titan-679817}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Sid Caesar, a King of Comedy, Dies at 91|url=https://people.com/celebrity/sid-caesar-dies/|accessdate=June 25, 2019|date=February 12, 2014|last=Silverman|first=Stephen M.|publisher=People Magazine|archive-date=2021-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415021436/https://people.com/celebrity/sid-caesar-dies/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=UPDATE 3-Comic legend Sid Caesar dies at 91|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/people-sidcaesar/update-3-comic-legend-sid-caesar-dies-at-91-idUSL2N0LH1RJ20140212|accessdate=June 26, 2019|date=February 12, 2014|last=Dobuzinskis|first=Alex|publisher=Reuters|archive-date=2021-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415021449/https://www.reuters.com/article/people-sidcaesar/update-3-comic-legend-sid-caesar-dies-at-91-idUSL2N0LH1RJ20140212}}</ref>。

